or</span>(number / <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>)\n  }\n  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> reverseNumber\n}\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">export</span> { <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ReverseNumber</span> }\n"
